"" Much of this is replicating the default bindings from Vimium

"" Set blank page on new tab
set newtab about:blank

" Keep accidentally closing/opening tab while attempting to move up/down
unbind d
unbind u

" Love this binding
bind yt tabduplicate

bind <C-w> tabdetach

bind x tabclose
bind X undo

" Reduce scroll distance (default 10)
bind j scrollline 5
bind k scrollline -5

colourscheme shydactyl

" Bookmark searching
bind --mode=normal b fillcmdline bmarks
bind --mode=normal B fillcmdline bmarks -t
